data.description: Charming mid-century home in Hilton Village. This home has beautiful hardwood floors, updated kitchen, solar panels, basement, fully encapsulated crawlspace with dehumidifier, and large fenced in backyard with garage/workshop. House is equipped with solar panels that will cover 100% of energy usage (plus an additional credit) in the summer and cover 75% of energy usage in the winter. Located just one block from the James River, near hospitals, shopping, and military bases.
